OMERO installation 
using Docker images written by openmicroscopy
https://github.com/ome/docker-example-omero

Docker-compose command includes images: 
omero-server
postgres
omero-web

How to start the omero server? Follow the docs.openmicroscopy.org. 
https://docs.openmicroscopy.org/omero/5.6.3/sysadmins/unix/server-installation.html


# Location of the OMERO.server
export OMERODIR=/opt/omero/server/OMERO.serverÂ¨

# To iniciate the 'omero' command, set up the envvar OMERO_VENV in the Docker container omero-server
OMERO_VENV=/opt/omero/server/venv3
export PATH=$PATH:$OMERO_VENV/bin/

